high_descs: turn right and face the counter in the corner
pick up the knife on the table behind the bread
face the table again in front of the potato
cut the potato behind the black cup on the table
place the knife down on the table in front of the tomato
turn right and face the counter top to the left of the oven
open the bottom cabinet door and take out the glass bowl next to the oven
turn left and return to the table next to the black door
place the bowl on the table behind the bread
pick up a slice of potato
put a slice of potato in the clear bowl
anns.task_desc: Slice a potato and obtain a bowl to prepare for the potato slice

high_descs: Move to stand in front of the door, facing the white table in the corner.
Pick up the sharp knife from the table that's behind the loaf of bread.
Move a step to the right while carrying the knife.
Slice the potato that's behind the coffee mug on the table.
Place the knife on the table in front of the tomato
Move to stand in front of the coffee maker, which is to the left of the stove.
Open the cupboard closest to the stove beneath the counter and pull out a clear bowl.
Carry the bowl back to the white table in the corner.
Place the bowl on the white table behind the loaf of bread and to the left of the sliced potato.
Pick up a slice of potato from the table.
Place the slice of potato in the clear bowl.
anns.task_desc: Place a slice of potato in a bowl from a cupboard by the stove.

high_descs: Walk to the loaf of bread on the table.
Pick up the yellow knife behind the bread on the table.
Take one step to the right and face the table.
Cut up the potato on the table.
Place the knife in front of the tomato on the table.
Turn right and walk to the cabinets below the coffee machine.
Pick up a glass bowl from the right cabinet below the coffee machine.
Turn left and walk to the white table in the corner.
Place the bowl behind the bread on the table.
Pick up a piece of potato from the table.
Place the piece of potato in the glass bowl on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a glass bowl with a piece of potato in it on the table across from the fridge.
